title.rendered: COREKEES PART OF THE AMSTERDAM CAPITAL HOUSE

content.rendered:
At the Amsterdam Capital House event, the start-up ecosystem comes together for the annual three-day (virtual) house. Placing founders at the core and creating space for meaningful connections, as they merge into the world of Human, Social & Financial Capital! Amsterdam Capital House is an annual event organized by Capital House. On a mission to create a closer ecosystem, actively supporting the growth of founders & entrepreneurs shaping our future.

This year, Corekees will be part of the Amsterdam Capital House event again on March 24, 25 and 26. Where as a participant, when purchasing an entrance ticket, at a session of your choice, you can leave a donation for the ACH’21 forest. The revenues from the trees always go to new trees: it is a self-multiplying forest.

through this link you can participate in one of the (virtual) house sessions.
